{"sections":{"main":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"use_theme_colors":true,"padding_top":36,"padding_bottom":36}},"rich_text_DYFY6n":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"title_HCgTzg":{"type":"title","settings":{"title":"","accent_text":"Contacteer ons:"}},"subtitle_9cc8dw":{"type":"subtitle","settings":{"subtitle":"<p>Via Whatsapp: +31 651255717<br\/>Via e-mail: support@petcura.nl<\/p>"}},"title_pw3da9":{"type":"title","settings":{"title":"","accent_text":"Vragen of feedback? Laat het ons weten!"}},"subtitle_4NmhnQ":{"type":"subtitle","settings":{"subtitle":"<p>Wij reageren altijd binnen 24u. Wegens drukte kunnen we momenteel geen telefonisch contact aanbieden. We zijn wél bereikbaar op WhatsApp en via e-mail.<\/p><p>Ben je dierenarts en wil je met ons samenwerken? Stuur ons een bericht, dan bekijken we samen de mogelijkheden.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["title_HCgTzg","subtitle_9cc8dw","title_pw3da9","subtitle_4NmhnQ"],"name":"Rich Text","settings":{"use_theme_colors":true,"text_alignment":"left","mobile_text_alignment":"left","padding_top":40,"padding_bottom":0,"padding_horizontal":20,"title_font_size":36,"title_font_size_mobile":28,"title_line_height":1.3,"title_margin_bottom":20,"title_color":"#000000","use_accent_gradient":false,"accent_color":"#ef4a65","accent_gradient_start":"#ef4a65","accent_gradient_end":"#ff6b35","accent_gradient_angle":45,"subtitle_font_size":18,"subtitle_font_size_mobile":16,"subtitle_line_height":1.6,"subtitle_margin_bottom":32,"subtitle_max_width":700,"subtitle_color":"#666666","button_font_size":16,"button_font_size_mobile":14,"button_padding_vertical":14,"button_padding_horizontal":28,"button_border_radius":4,"button_border_width":0,"button_margin_top":24,"button_bg_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_border_color":"#000000","button_hover_bg_color":"#333333","button_hover_text_color":"#ffffff","section_bg_color":"#ffffff","section_border_radius":0}},"form":{"type":"contact-form","settings":{"use_theme_colors":false,"heading":"","heading_size":"h2","background_color":"#ffffff","heading_color":"#000000","text_color":"#000000","field_background_color":"#ffffff","field_border_color":"#e5e5e5","field_text_color":"#000000","placeholder_color":"#999999","button_background_color":"#000000","button_text_color":"#ffffff","button_hover_background_color":"#333333","success_color":"#28a745","error_color":"#dc3545","use_global_button_styling":true,"override_global_border_radius":false,"input_border_radius":0,"textarea_border_radius":0,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":36}},"testimonials_iRHRgG":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"testimonial_xm4dwP":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Geen loze woorden: PetCura is écht top","content":"<p>Sinds mijn Tibetaanse Terrier vriend PetCura gebruikt, merk ik duidelijk vooruitgang. Geen startstijfheid meer, geen pijnlijke gewrichten en Skyler loopt veel soepeler. De levering was snel en alles werd netjes verpakt. Ik blijf zeker bestellen van PetCura.<\/p>","author_name":"Marieke Vos","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"4 uur geleden"}},"testimonial_p3ajEE":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Supplement doet wat het belooft!","content":"<p>Mijn Husky van 15 jaar, Micha, had moeite met opstaan en traplopen. Sinds ik PetCura ‘Heup & Gewrichten’ gebruik, zie ik een enorme verbetering, en zie ik ook een enorm verschil in haar speelplezier. Ze speelt weer buiten alsof ze jaren jonger is. Een aanrader!<\/p>","author_name":"Sophie De Lint","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":false,"purchase_date":"1 dag geleden"}},"testimonial_wRgrcB":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Sinds 2,5 maand geef ik het","content":"<p>Ik geef mijn twee Border Collies nu 2,5 maand de snacks van PetCura en hun beweging is zichtbaar soepeler. Minder stijf, makkelijker stappen en weer meer energie. Wij zijn supertevreden. !😊<\/p>","author_name":"Chantal De Bruyn","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"4 dagen geleden"}},"testimonial_FJpJkX":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Snel geleverd en binnen een paar weken al verschil","content":"<p>Mijn hond liep de laatste tijd wat stroef en leek minder zin te hebben in wandelen. Na twee weken PetCura zag ik al verandering: hij staat sneller op, loopt soepeler en lijkt echt meer plezier te hebben buiten. Zelfs traplopen, waar hij altijd moeite mee had, gaat duidelijk beter.<\/p>","author_name":"Yara Willems","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"1 week geleden"}},"testimonial_HbAGgX":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Eindelijk verbetering bij onze hond met stijve gewrichten","content":"<p>Onze hond had al langer problemen met stijfheid en beperkte flexibiliteit. We hadden meerdere supplementen geprobeerd zonder echt resultaat. Met PetCura zagen we na een paar weken wél een duidelijk verschil: ze komt veel makkelijker overeind en lijkt minder pijn te hebben.<\/p>","author_name":"Marco Jansen","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"1 maand geleden"}},"testimonial_f4MXYN":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Onze hond van 9 jaar loopt weer alsof hij jonger is","content":"<p>Ik had eerlijk gezegd niet verwacht dat het zoveel zou helpen. Mijn hond van 9 had last van artrose en werd steeds minder actief. Nu zien we hem weer spelen, rennen en kwispelen als we de riem pakken. De stijfheid na het slapen is bijna weg. Wij zijn écht heel tevreden.<\/p>","author_name":"Jordy van Loon","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"1 maand geleden"}},"testimonial_EgD3dz":{"type":"testimonial","settings":{"show_stars":true,"title":"Echt een prima product","content":"<p>Snelle levering en duidelijke informatie. Mijn hond liep erg stroef maar na gebruik van PetCura beweegt hij weer veel soepeler. Het helpt echt.<\/p>","author_name":"Frank Rutgers","rating":5,"verified":true,"show_purchase_date":true,"purchase_date":"2 weken geleden"}}},"block_order":["testimonial_xm4dwP","testimonial_p3ajEE","testimonial_wRgrcB","testimonial_FJpJkX","testimonial_HbAGgX","testimonial_f4MXYN","testimonial_EgD3dz"],"disabled":true,"name":"Testimonials","settings":{"use_theme_colors":false,"section_background":"linear-gradient(54deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 1), rgba(255, 255, 255, 1) 100%)","heading_color":"#181b1d","subtitle_color":"#888888","text_color":"#181b1d","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":20,"heading":"","heading_size":40,"heading_size_mobile":40,"heading_accent":"","subtitle":"","subtitle_size":18,"override_global_accent":true,"accent_color":"#ef4a65","use_accent_gradient":false,"accent_text_gradient":"linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(113, 172, 194, 1), rgba(180, 225, 237, 1) 100%)","accent_font_family":"inherit","accent_font_style":"normal","accent_font_weight":"300","accent_text_margin_left":0,"use_trustpilot_stars":true,"trustpilot_star_color":"#c6fa54","trustpilot_star_empty_color":"#dcdce6","testimonial_title_size":18,"testimonial_title_size_mobile":16,"testimonial_content_size":14,"testimonial_content_size_mobile":14,"author_name_size":13,"author_avatar_text_size":17,"verified_badge_size":13,"verified_badge_size_mobile":13,"verified_icon_size":14,"purchase_date_size":12,"purchase_date_size_mobile":12,"card_rating_size":16,"show_rating":true,"enable_mask_fade":false,"rating_summary_text":"<p>Uitstekend<strong> 4.8\/5 <\/strong>|<strong> <\/strong>Gebaseerd op 7.135 reviews<\/p>","rating_value":4.8,"rating_max":5,"summary_star_color":"#05b67a","summary_star_empty_color":"#707070","rating_summary_text_color":"#fdffff","star_color":"#05b67a","star_empty_color":"#707070","rating_summary_bg_color":"#ffffff","rating_summary_background":"linear-gradient(310deg, rgba(25, 67, 67, 1), rgba(23, 67, 60, 1) 100%)","enable_rating_summary_border":false,"rating_summary_border_width":1,"rating_su